document.full_text: american stacy lewis overhauled world number one yani tseng to claim the year's first major and her maiden lpga tour title with a three-shot victory at the kraft nabisco championship sunday.
document.title: lewis overhauls tseng to claim year's first major
lines_and_colors: american stacy lewis overhauled world number one yani tseng to claim the year's first major and her maiden lpga tour title with a three-shot victory at the kraft nabisco championship sunday.
